full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/27/2023 The University of the Panjab. THE PUNJAB The Matriculation and School Leaving Certificate Examination. SESSION 1925. - This is to certify that Upal and student son of 3. Bheja Singh of the Khalsa passed in / the First Division, the Matriculation and School Leaving Certificate Examination of the Panjab University held in Manch 1925 Passed also Or , additional Subject. Date of Birth January, 1906. Senate haff, Labore: 7.6 REGISTRAR, The 1st August, 1925 University of the Panjab.
